        "email": "yawei.niu@intel.com",
        "username": "niu",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-12-26 10:41:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n\"do_node $node $cmd 2>&1 | tee $log\", probably because the $log is the output on client but the \"DNE mode isn't supported\" is on mds?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 5
    },
